OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779390672
OL,3,CStarmer says he 'wants to be a part
OL,4,Cof' Burnham's Makerfield campaign
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has said he wants to
OL,7,F"be a part of" the Makerfield by-
OL,8,Felection campaign for potential Labour
OL,9,FParty leadership challenger Andy
OL,10,FBurnham.
OL,12,FOn a visit to Essex, the prime
OL,13,Fminister told broadcasters he wanted
OL,14,Fthe "whole Labour movement" to be
OL,15,Finvolved, saying it would be "a
OL,16,Fstraight fight between Labour and
OL,17,FReform".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779390672
OL,3,CStarmer says he 'wants to be a part
OL,4,Cof' Burnham's Makerfield campaign
OL,6,FHe said: "It's about the values that
OL,7,Fwe take into politics, and it's really
OL,8,Fimportant that we pull together and
OL,9,Ffight in that by-election, as we will
OL,10,Fdo."
OL,12,FIn response, Andy Burnham's office
OL,13,Fwelcomed this offer and a spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "Anyone who wants to embrace
OL,15,FAndy's campaign message is welcome on
OL,16,Fthe campaign."
OL,18,FWhen questioned by ITV News on
OL,19,FThursday morning, the PM refused to
OL,20,Fcomment on whether he would take on
OL,21,FAndy Burnham in a leadership race.
