OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779390672
OL,3,CStarmer says he 'wants to be a part
OL,4,Cof' Burnham's Makerfield campaign
OL,6,FStarmer was instead keen to draw
OL,7,Fattention to "delivery" after
OL,8,Fstatistics released earlier showed
OL,9,Fthat net migration has fallen to the
OL,10,Flowest level since 2012, excluding the
OL,11,Fpandemic.
OL,13,FHe also chose to highlight the
OL,14,Fgovernment announcements on summer
OL,15,Fsavings.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
