OL,3,CStarmer says he 'wants to be a part
OL,4,Cof' Burnham's Makerfield campaign
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves announced a
OL,7,Fplan that will cut VAT from 20% to 5%
OL,8,Fon ticket prices for both adults and
OL,9,Fchildren for attractions such as
OL,10,Ffairs, theme parks, zoos and museums,
OL,11,Fas well as on children's tickets for
OL,12,Fcinemas, concerts, soft play, theatre
OL,13,Fand meals in restaurants and cafes.
OL,15,FReeves has called the raft of measures
OL,16,Fthe 'Great British Summer Savings
OL,17,FScheme', also announcing she will
OL,18,Fincrease tax-free mileage rates by 10p
OL,19,Fper mile, backdated to April 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
