OL,3,CStarmer says he 'wants to be a part
OL,4,Cof' Burnham's Makerfield campaign
OL,6,FThe PM added that it has "only been
OL,7,Fpossible because of the steps we took
OL,8,Fon the budget, the fact that inflation
OL,9,Fdropped is because of the steps."
OL,11,FHe insisted "that didn't drop out of
OL,12,Fthe sky ` that's because of the
OL,13,Fdecisions the Government took."
OL,15,FHe added: "So, we've got a very good
OL,16,Fstory to tell."
