OL,3,CStarmer says he 'wants to be a part
OL,4,Cof' Burnham's Makerfield campaign
OL,6,FThe Green Party announced their
OL,7,Fcandidate for the by-election on
OL,8,FThursday, but hours later revealed he
OL,9,Fhad withdrawn for "personal and family
OL,10,Freasons".
OL,12,FCandidates have until Tuesday, May 26
OL,13,Fto declare.
OL,15,FThe current list of candidates is:
OL,17,FLabour - Andy Burnham
OL,19,FMonster Raving Loony Party - Alan
OL,20,F'Howlin' Laud Hope
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
